# Keep the build context lean — these never need to enter any image.

# .NET build artifacts
**/bin
**/obj
**/TestResults
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea

# Node / Vite
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/coverage
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# API-staged client output (rebuilt inside the image)
src/RecordKeeping.Api/wwwroot

# Git / OS / editor
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini

# Docs not needed for the runtime image
*.md
docs/

# Local dev secrets
*.env
*.env.local
secrets.json
